metadata.name: ronin
metadata.description:
Ronin //

a drifter, wanderer, transient, a vagabond

a samurai without a master
left by himself to maintain order
an order only he is accountable for
an order only he knows

he lives to uphold a code left only to him
to carry a torch
of a light only he can see
on a journey a drifter would know

–

Bids above .5 Ξ will receive a canvas print of this artwork.

this is artwork is the cover art for GTDyneMusiq's single 'Ronin'
